name: sphinx-panels
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "sphinx-panels" %}
{% set version = "0.6.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d36dcd26358117e11888f7143db4ac2301ebe90873ac00627bf1fe526bf0f058

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
    - setuptools
  run:
    - docutils
    - python >=3.6
    - sphinx >=2,<5

test:
  requires:
    - pip
  imports:
    - sphinx_panels
  commands:
    - python -m pip check

about:
  home: https://github.com/executablebooks/sphinx-panels
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A sphinx extension for creating panels in a grid layout.
  doc_url: https://sphinx-panels.readthedocs.io/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - choldgraf
